12
00:02:16,950 --> 00:02:19,450
<i>Krećemo.</i>

13
00:02:22,962 --> 00:02:25,601
FBI. Otvarajte. -Otvarajte!

14
00:02:27,404 --> 00:02:31,843
Ruke gore! Na zemlju!
